'''Bahrom''' (2020 - 2025) was an Iranian Persian cat who lived a dangerous life in the streets of Tehran. 

==Life==
Bahrom was born in Tehran beneath an outdoor amphitheater stage during an Olivia Rodrigo concert. He allegedly had a "wild" first few hours of his life, which supposedly involved him getting separated from his parents. Bahrom started off as a stray on شارع المركز (Center Avenue), sharing the street with four other cats named Freshteh, Quasem, Satrapi, and Tirdad, and a rat named Butters.

